[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/weak_twos"]
[Student "S"]
{NORTH is unsure whether to bid game or not, so he bids 2NT to get more information about 
SOUTH's hand.

SOUTH's 3\S is discouraging, a hand below average in strength and no outside high card.

NORTH passes and hopes for the best.}

