[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/weak_twos"]
[Student "S"]
{WEST has no way to tell whether EAST can provide one winner or not.

So she takes the bold approach and bids 4\H.

If the opening lead is a \S or a \D then WEST 
will probably make the game. Otherwise she will likely go down one.}

