[Category "Partnership Bidding"]
[Difficulty "intermediate"]
[SkillPath "partnership_bidding/weak_twos"]
[Student "S"]
{EAST responds 2NT, asking for more information. 

When WEST shows a decent hand with a high \C EAST should bid 3NT.}

